{
  "video_id": "waRC-CQnoeY",
  "title": "If a story moves you, act on it | Sisonke Msimang",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 14400.0,
      "text": "So earlier this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14400.0,
      "end_time": 18240.0,
      "text": "I was informed that I would be doing a TED Talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18240.0,
      "end_time": 20240.0,
      "text": "So I was excited, then I panicked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20240.0,
      "end_time": 22280.0,
      "text": "then I was excited, then I panicked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22280.0,
      "end_time": 24840.0,
      "text": "and in between the excitement and the panicking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24840.0,
      "end_time": 27160.0,
      "text": "I started to do my research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27160.0,
      "end_time": 31640.0,
      "text": "and my research primarily consisted of Googling how to give a great TED Talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31640.0,
      "end_time": 32880.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32880.0,
      "end_time": 34560.0,
      "text": "And interspersed with that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34560.0,
      "end_time": 37280.0,
      "text": "I was Googling Chimamanda Ngozi Adichie."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37280.0,
      "end_time": 38920.0,
      "text": "How many of you know who that is?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38920.0,
      "end_time": 41720.0,
      "text": "(Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41720.0,
      "end_time": 44080.0,
      "text": "So I was Googling her because I always Google her"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44080.0,
      "end_time": 45360.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;m just a fan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 45360.0,
      "end_time": 49000.0,
      "text": "but also because she always has important and interesting things to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49000.0,
      "end_time": 52480.0,
      "text": "And the combination of those searches"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52480.0,
      "end_time": 55120.0,
      "text": "kept leading me to her talk"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55120.0,
      "end_time": 58320.0,
      "text": "on the dangers of a single story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58320.0,
      "end_time": 61720.0,
      "text": "on what happens when we have a solitary lens"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61720.0,
      "end_time": 64240.0,
      "text": "through which to understand certain groups of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64239.99999999999,
      "end_time": 67720.0,
      "text": "and it is the perfect talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67720.0,
      "end_time": 72080.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the talk that I would have given if I had been famous first."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72080.0,
      "end_time": 74280.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 74280.0,
      "end_time": 77680.0,
      "text": "You know, and you know, like, she&#39;s African and I&#39;m African,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77680.0,
      "end_time": 79640.0,
      "text": "and she&#39;s a feminist and I&#39;m a feminist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 79640.0,
      "end_time": 81840.0,
      "text": "and she&#39;s a storyteller and I&#39;m a storyteller,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 81840.0,
      "end_time": 83680.0,
      "text": "so I really felt like it&#39;s my talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 83680.0,
      "end_time": 86440.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86440.0,
      "end_time": 89760.0,
      "text": "So I decided that I was going to learn how to code,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89760.0,
      "end_time": 91800.0,
      "text": "and then I was going to hack the internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91800.0,
      "end_time": 95560.0,
      "text": "and I would take down all the copies of that talk that existed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95560.0,
      "end_time": 97000.0,
      "text": "and then I would memorize it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 97000.0,
      "end_time": 100280.0,
      "text": "and then I would come here and deliver it as if it was my own speech."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100280.0,
      "end_time": 103480.0,
      "text": "So that plan was going really well, except the coding part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 103480.0,
      "end_time": 107400.0,
      "text": "and then one morning a few months ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107400.0,
      "end_time": 109000.0,
      "text": "I woke up"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109000.0,
      "end_time": 114480.0,
      "text": "to the news that the wife of a certain presidential candidate"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 114480.0,
      "end_time": 117480.0,
      "text": "had given a speech that --"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117480.0,
      "end_time": 119440.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119440.0,
      "end_time": 124960.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124960.0,
      "end_time": 129600.0,
      "text": "that sounded eerily like a speech given by one of my other faves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 129600.0,
      "end_time": 130840.0,
      "text": "Michelle Obama."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 130840.0,
      "end_time": 132960.0,
      "text": "(Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 132960.0,
      "end_time": 137000.0,
      "text": "And so I decided that I should probably write my own TED Talk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 137000.0,
      "end_time": 139520.0,
      "text": "and so that is what I am here to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 139520.0,
      "end_time": 144640.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m here to talk about my own observations about storytelling."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 144640.0,
      "end_time": 148640.0,
      "text": "I want to talk to you about the power of stories, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 148640.0,
      "end_time": 151600.0,
      "text": "but I also want to talk about their limitations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 151600.0,
      "end_time": 156280.0,
      "text": "particularly for those of us who are interested in social justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 156280.0,
      "end_time": 159200.0,
      "text": "So since Adichie gave that talk seven years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 159200.0,
      "end_time": 161480.0,
      "text": "there has been a boom in storytelling."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 161480.0,
      "end_time": 164240.0,
      "text": "Stories are everywhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 164240.0,
      "end_time": 168200.0,
      "text": "and if there was a danger in the telling of one tired old tale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 168200.0,
      "end_time": 172560.0,
      "text": "then I think there has got to be lots to celebrate about the flourishing"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 172560.0,
      "end_time": 175360.0,
      "text": "of so many stories and so many voices."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 175360.0,
      "end_time": 178960.0,
      "text": "Stories are the antidote to bias."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 178960.0,
      "end_time": 184040.0,
      "text": "In fact, today, if you are middle class and connected via the internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 184040.0,
      "end_time": 187200.0,
      "text": "you can download stories at the touch of a button"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 187200.0,
      "end_time": 188600.0,
      "text": "or the swipe of a screen."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 188600.0,
      "end_time": 190440.0,
      "text": "You can listen to a podcast"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 190440.0,
      "end_time": 194360.0,
      "text": "about what it&#39;s like to grow up Dalit in Kolkata."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 194360.0,
      "end_time": 196880.0,
      "text": "You can hear an indigenous man in Australia"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 196880.0,
      "end_time": 201000.0,
      "text": "talk about the trials and triumphs of raising his children in dignity"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 201000.0,
      "end_time": 202360.0,
      "text": "and in pride."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 202360.0,
      "end_time": 204360.0,
      "text": "Stories make us fall in love."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 204360.0,
      "end_time": 207560.0,
      "text": "They heal rifts and they bridge divides."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 207560.0,
      "end_time": 209440.0,
      "text": "Stories can even make it easier for us"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 209440.0,
      "end_time": 212120.0,
      "text": "to talk about the deaths of people in our societies"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 212120.0,
      "end_time": 214600.0,
      "text": "who don&#39;t matter, because they make us care."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 214600.0,
      "end_time": 216800.0,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 216800.0,
      "end_time": 218080.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not so sure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 218080.0,
      "end_time": 221840.0,
      "text": "and I actually work for a place called the Centre for Stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 221840.0,
      "end_time": 226280.0,
      "text": "And my job is to help to tell stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 226280.0,
      "end_time": 229840.0,
      "text": "that challenge mainstream narratives about what it means to be black"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 229840.0,
      "end_time": 232920.0,
      "text": "or a Muslim or a refugee or any of those other categories"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 232920.0,
      "end_time": 235960.0,
      "text": "that we talk about all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 235960.0,
      "end_time": 237200.0,
      "text": "But I come to this work"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 237200.0,
      "end_time": 240720.0,
      "text": "after a long history as a social justice activist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 240720.0,
      "end_time": 242880.0,
      "text": "and so I&#39;m really interested in the ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 242880.0,
      "end_time": 245600.0,
      "text": "that people talk about nonfiction storytelling"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 245600.0,
      "end_time": 247960.0,
      "text": "as though it&#39;s about more than entertainment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 247960.0,
      "end_time": 251560.0,
      "text": "as though it&#39;s about being a catalyst for social action."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 251560.0,
      "end_time": 254240.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not uncommon to hear people say"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 254240.0,
      "end_time": 258960.0,
      "text": "that stories make the world a better place."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 258959.99999999997,
      "end_time": 262200.0,
      "text": "Increasingly, though, I worry that even the most poignant stories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 262200.0,
      "end_time": 266160.0,
      "text": "particularly the stories about people who no one seems to care about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 266160.0,
      "end_time": 269600.0,
      "text": "can often get in the way of action towards social justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 269600.0,
      "end_time": 273440.0,
      "text": "Now, this is not because storytellers mean any harm."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 273440.0,
      "end_time": 274720.0,
      "text": "Quite the contrary."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 274720.0,
      "end_time": 279600.0,
      "text": "Storytellers are often do-gooders like me and, I suspect, yourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 279600.0,
      "end_time": 282680.0,
      "text": "And the audiences of storytellers"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 282680.0,
      "end_time": 286360.0,
      "text": "are often deeply compassionate and empathetic people."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 286360.0,
      "end_time": 291200.0,
      "text": "Still, good intentions can have unintended consequences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 291200.0,
      "end_time": 295680.0,
      "text": "and so I want to propose that stories are not as magical as they seem."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 295680.0,
      "end_time": 298600.0,
      "text": "So three -- because it&#39;s always got to be three --"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 298600.0,
      "end_time": 300840.0,
      "text": "three reasons why I think"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 300840.0,
      "end_time": 306320.0,
      "text": "that stories don&#39;t necessarily make the world a better place."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 306320.0,
      "end_time": 310400.0,
      "text": "Firstly, stories can create an illusion of solidarity."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 310400.0,
      "end_time": 312960.0,
      "text": "There is nothing like that feel-good factor you get"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 312960.0,
      "end_time": 315120.0,
      "text": "from listening to a fantastic story"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 315120.0,
      "end_time": 318520.0,
      "text": "where you feel like you climbed that mountain, right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 318520.0,
      "end_time": 321840.0,
      "text": "or that you befriended that death row inmate."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 321840.0,
      "end_time": 323280.0,
      "text": "But you didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 323280.0,
      "end_time": 325120.0,
      "text": "You haven&#39;t done anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 325120.0,
      "end_time": 326920.0,
      "text": "Listening is an important"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 326920.0,
      "end_time": 331120.0,
      "text": "but insufficient step towards social action."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 331120.0,
      "end_time": 334000.0,
      "text": "Secondly, I think often we are drawn"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 334000.0,
      "end_time": 336960.0,
      "text": "towards characters and protagonists"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 336960.0,
      "end_time": 340440.0,
      "text": "who are likable and human."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 340440.0,
      "end_time": 342360.0,
      "text": "And this makes sense, of course, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 342360.0,
      "end_time": 345440.0,
      "text": "Because if you like someone, then you care about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 345440.0,
      "end_time": 347400.0,
      "text": "But the inverse is also true."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 347400.0,
      "end_time": 349200.0,
      "text": "If you don&#39;t like someone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 349200.0,
      "end_time": 351160.0,
      "text": "then you don&#39;t care about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 351160.0,
      "end_time": 353040.0,
      "text": "And if you don&#39;t care about them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 353040.0,
      "end_time": 356960.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t have to see yourself as having a moral obligation"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 356960.0,
      "end_time": 361000.0,
      "text": "to think about the circumstances that shaped their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 361000.0,
      "end_time": 364320.0,
      "text": "I learned this lesson when I was 14 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 364320.0,
      "end_time": 367120.0,
      "text": "I learned that actually, you don&#39;t have to like someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 367120.0,
      "end_time": 368520.0,
      "text": "to recognize their wisdom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 368520.0,
      "end_time": 370640.0,
      "text": "and you certainly don&#39;t have to like someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 370640.0,
      "end_time": 372800.0,
      "text": "to take a stand by their side."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 372800.0,
      "end_time": 375520.0,
      "text": "So my bike was stolen"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 375520.0,
      "end_time": 377000.0,
      "text": "while I was riding it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 377000.0,
      "end_time": 378160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 378160.0,
      "end_time": 381760.0,
      "text": "which is possible if you&#39;re riding slowly enough, which I was."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 381760.0,
      "end_time": 383280.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 383280.0,
      "end_time": 386280.0,
      "text": "So one minute I&#39;m cutting across this field"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 386280.0,
      "end_time": 388600.0,
      "text": "in the Nairobi neighborhood where I grew up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 388600.0,
      "end_time": 391080.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s like a very bumpy path,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 391080.0,
      "end_time": 392920.0,
      "text": "and so when you&#39;re riding a bike,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 392920.0,
      "end_time": 395200.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t want to be like, you know --"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 395200.0,
      "end_time": 398160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 398160.0,
      "end_time": 402800.0,
      "text": "And so I&#39;m going like this, slowly pedaling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 402800.0,
      "end_time": 405400.0,
      "text": "and all of a sudden, I&#39;m on the floor."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 405400.0,
      "end_time": 407600.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m on the ground, and I look up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 407600.0,
      "end_time": 410400.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s this kid peddling away in the getaway vehicle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 410400.0,
      "end_time": 411920.0,
      "text": "which is my bike,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 411920.0,
      "end_time": 415200.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s about 11 or 12 years old, and I&#39;m on the floor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 415200.0,
      "end_time": 418080.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m crying because I saved a lot of money for that bike,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 418080.0,
      "end_time": 420680.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m crying and I stand up and I start screaming."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 420680.0,
      "end_time": 424960.0,
      "text": "Instinct steps in, and I start screaming, &quot;Mwizi, mwizi!&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 424960.0,
      "end_time": 427560.0,
      "text": "which means &quot;thief&quot; in Swahili."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 427560.0,
      "end_time": 432600.0,
      "text": "And out of the woodworks, all of these people come out"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 432600.0,
      "end_time": 434040.0,
      "text": "and they start to give chase."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 434040.0,
      "end_time": 436320.0,
      "text": "This is Africa, so mob justice in action."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 436320.0,
      "end_time": 437800.0,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 437800.0,
      "end_time": 440600.0,
      "text": "And I round the corner, and they&#39;ve captured him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 440600.0,
      "end_time": 442080.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve caught him."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 442080.0,
      "end_time": 444160.0,
      "text": "The suspect has been apprehended,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 444160.0,
      "end_time": 447760.0,
      "text": "and they make him give me my bike back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 447760.0,
      "end_time": 449400.0,
      "text": "and they also make him apologize."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 449400.0,
      "end_time": 453000.0,
      "text": "Again, you know, typical African justice, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 453000.0,
      "end_time": 454520.0,
      "text": "And so they make him say sorry."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 454520.0,
      "end_time": 456880.0,
      "text": "And so we stand there facing each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 456880.0,
      "end_time": 459840.0,
      "text": "and he looks at me, and he says sorry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 459840.0,
      "end_time": 463360.0,
      "text": "but he looks at me with this unbridled fury."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 463360.0,
      "end_time": 467440.0,
      "text": "He is very, very angry."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 467440.0,
      "end_time": 470520.0,
      "text": "And it is the first time that I have been confronted with someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 470520.0,
      "end_time": 473160.0,
      "text": "who doesn&#39;t like me simply because of what I represent."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 473160.0,
      "end_time": 475240.0,
      "text": "He looks at me with this look as if to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 475240.0,
      "end_time": 481240.0,
      "text": "&quot;You, with your shiny skin and your bike, you&#39;re angry at me?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 481240.0,
      "end_time": 484520.0,
      "text": "So it was a hard lesson that he didn&#39;t like me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 484520.0,
      "end_time": 486600.0,
      "text": "but you know what, he was right."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 486600.0,
      "end_time": 490120.0,
      "text": "I was a middle-class kid living in a poor country."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 490120.0,
      "end_time": 493760.0,
      "text": "I had a bike, and he barely had food."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 493760.0,
      "end_time": 496720.0,
      "text": "Sometimes, it&#39;s the messages that we don&#39;t want to hear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 496720.0,
      "end_time": 499240.0,
      "text": "the ones that make us want to crawl out of ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 499240.0,
      "end_time": 501840.0,
      "text": "that we need to hear the most."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 501840.0,
      "end_time": 505040.0,
      "text": "For every lovable storyteller who steals your heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 505040.0,
      "end_time": 509440.0,
      "text": "there are hundreds more whose voices are slurred and ragged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 509440.0,
      "end_time": 514640.0,
      "text": "who don&#39;t get to stand up on a stage dressed in fine clothes like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 514640.0,
      "end_time": 518960.0,
      "text": "There are a million angry-boy-on-a-bike stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 518960.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520640.00000000006,
      "text": "and we can&#39;t afford to ignore them"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 520640.0,
      "end_time": 523800.0,
      "text": "simply because we don&#39;t like their protagonists"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 523799.99999999994,
      "end_time": 526760.0,
      "text": "or because that&#39;s not the kid that we would bring home with us"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 526760.0,
      "end_time": 528600.0,
      "text": "from the orphanage."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 528600.0,
      "end_time": 530480.0,
      "text": "The third reason that I think"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 530480.0,
      "end_time": 534120.0,
      "text": "that stories don&#39;t necessarily make the world a better place"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 534120.0,
      "end_time": 537600.0,
      "text": "is that too often we are so invested in the personal narrative"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 537600.0,
      "end_time": 540880.0,
      "text": "that we forget to look at the bigger picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 540880.0,
      "end_time": 542800.0,
      "text": "And so we applaud someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 542800.0,
      "end_time": 545480.0,
      "text": "when they tell us about their feelings of shame,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 545480.0,
      "end_time": 549080.0,
      "text": "but we don&#39;t necessarily link that to oppression."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 549080.0,
      "end_time": 552760.0,
      "text": "We nod understandingly when someone says they felt small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 552760.0,
      "end_time": 555600.0,
      "text": "but we don&#39;t link that to discrimination."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 555600.0,
      "end_time": 558440.0,
      "text": "The most important stories, especially for social justice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 558440.0,
      "end_time": 560280.0,
      "text": "are those that do both,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 560280.0,
      "end_time": 565920.0,
      "text": "that are both personal and allow us to explore and understand the political."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 565920.0,
      "end_time": 567960.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not just about the stories we like"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 567960.0,
      "end_time": 569880.0,
      "text": "versus the stories we choose to ignore."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 569880.0,
      "end_time": 573840.0,
      "text": "Increasingly, we are living in a society where there are larger forces at play,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 573840.0,
      "end_time": 578640.0,
      "text": "where stories are actually for many people beginning to replace the news."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 578640.0,
      "end_time": 579880.0,
      "text": "Yeah?"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 579880.0,
      "end_time": 583280.0,
      "text": "We live in a time where we are witnessing the decline of facts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 583280.0,
      "end_time": 585520.0,
      "text": "when emotions rule"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 585520.0,
      "end_time": 588640.0,
      "text": "and analysis, it&#39;s kind of boring, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 588640.0,
      "end_time": 594040.0,
      "text": "Where we value what we feel more than what we actually know."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 594040.0,
      "end_time": 598360.0,
      "text": "A recent report by the Pew Center on trends in America"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 598360.0,
      "end_time": 604160.0,
      "text": "indicates that only 10 percent of young adults under the age of 30"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 604160.0,
      "end_time": 607560.0,
      "text": "&quot;place a lot of trust in the media.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 607560.0,
      "end_time": 609840.0,
      "text": "Now, this is significant."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 609840.0,
      "end_time": 612480.0,
      "text": "It means that storytellers are gaining trust"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 612480.0,
      "end_time": 613880.0,
      "text": "at precisely the same moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 613880.0,
      "end_time": 618040.0,
      "text": "that many in the media are losing the confidence in the public."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 618040.0,
      "end_time": 620640.0,
      "text": "This is not a good thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 620640.0,
      "end_time": 622440.0,
      "text": "because while stories are important"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 622440.0,
      "end_time": 624680.0,
      "text": "and they help us to have insights in many ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 624680.0,
      "end_time": 626560.0,
      "text": "we need the media."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 626560.0,
      "end_time": 629080.0,
      "text": "From my years as a social justice activist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 629080.0,
      "end_time": 635200.0,
      "text": "I know very well that we need credible facts from media institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 635200.0,
      "end_time": 639240.0,
      "text": "combined with the powerful voices of storytellers."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 639240.0,
      "end_time": 643840.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what pushes the needle forward in terms of social justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 643840.0,
      "end_time": 648480.0,
      "text": "In the final analysis, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 648480.0,
      "end_time": 650320.0,
      "text": "it is justice"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 650320.0,
      "end_time": 652080.0,
      "text": "that makes the world a better place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 652080.0,
      "end_time": 655080.0,
      "text": "not stories. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 655080.0,
      "end_time": 658160.0,
      "text": "And so if it is justice that we are after,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 658160.0,
      "end_time": 661600.0,
      "text": "then I think we mustn&#39;t focus on the media or on storytellers."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 661600.0,
      "end_time": 664320.0,
      "text": "We must focus on audiences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 664320.0,
      "end_time": 667440.0,
      "text": "on anyone who has ever turned on a radio"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 667440.0,
      "end_time": 669280.0,
      "text": "or listened to a podcast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 669280.0,
      "end_time": 671400.0,
      "text": "and that means all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 671400.0,
      "end_time": 673560.0,
      "text": "So a few concluding thoughts"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 673560.0,
      "end_time": 678000.0,
      "text": "on what audiences can do to make the world a better place."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 678000.0,
      "end_time": 681960.0,
      "text": "So firstly, the world would be a better place, I think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 681960.0,
      "end_time": 685560.0,
      "text": "if audiences were more curious and more skeptical"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 685560.0,
      "end_time": 688200.0,
      "text": "and asked more questions about the social context"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 688200.0,
      "end_time": 692200.0,
      "text": "that created those stories that they love so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 692200.0,
      "end_time": 694480.0,
      "text": "Secondly, the world would be a better place"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 694480.0,
      "end_time": 699640.0,
      "text": "if audiences recognized that storytelling is intellectual work."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 699640.0,
      "end_time": 702600.0,
      "text": "And I think it would be important for audiences"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 702600.0,
      "end_time": 707960.0,
      "text": "to demand more buttons on their favorite websites,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 707960.0,
      "end_time": 710680.0,
      "text": "buttons for example that say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 710680.0,
      "end_time": 712320.0,
      "text": "&quot;If you liked this story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 712320.0,
      "end_time": 716400.0,
      "text": "click here to support a cause your storyteller believes in.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 716400.0,
      "end_time": 722480.0,
      "text": "Or &quot;click here to contribute to your storyteller&#39;s next big idea.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 722480.0,
      "end_time": 725080.0,
      "text": "Often, we are committed to the platforms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 725080.0,
      "end_time": 727560.0,
      "text": "but not necessarily to the storytellers themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 727560.0,
      "end_time": 732680.0,
      "text": "And then lastly, I think that audiences can make the world a better place"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 732680.0,
      "end_time": 735560.0,
      "text": "by switching off their phones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 735560.0,
      "end_time": 737600.0,
      "text": "by stepping away from their screens"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 737600.0,
      "end_time": 742840.0,
      "text": "and stepping out into the real world beyond what feels safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 742840.0,
      "end_time": 744880.0,
      "text": "Alice Walker has said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 744880.0,
      "end_time": 748680.0,
      "text": "&quot;Look closely at the present you are constructing."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 748680.0,
      "end_time": 752640.0,
      "text": "It should look like the future you are dreaming.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 752640.0,
      "end_time": 754880.0,
      "text": "Storytellers can help us to dream,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 754880.0,
      "end_time": 759480.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s up to all of us to have a plan for justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 759480.0,
      "end_time": 760720.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 760720.0,
      "end_time": 770720.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}